  "texts": [
    "Here we report the best performing training method in Difficult SD, Difficult RS and Novel RS setting.",
    "The complete results can be found in Table 11 (for Llama-2) and Table 12 (for Llama-3.1).",
    "The Concept score values are shown in Figure 2.",
    "We find that at least one vocabulary adaptation strategy improves over BASE in a total of five out of six settings (LLM-Dataset pairs).",
    "The overall average improvement for 18.75% for Llama-2 and 14.82% for Llama-3.1 models across datasets."
